 What? 

8
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:57,370
Supervisor Ha was found with his dead father when he was little

9
00:00:57,370 --> 00:01:02,670
and the corpse of his father, Ha Seong Jin, looked lifeless and strange?

10
00:01:02,670 --> 00:01:05,410
 She is with Supervisor Ha. 

11
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:08,900
 She is in danger. Grave danger. 

12
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,040
Supervisor Ha, you are under arrest for the guards' corpse incident

13
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:18,470
at Inwang Mountain.

14
00:01:19,340 --> 00:01:22,280
No! Don't do this.

15
00:01:22,290 --> 00:01:25,630
- There must be a mistake. 
 - Step aside.

16
00:01:25,630 --> 00:01:27,840
Your Highness, why are you doing this?

17
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,710
I told you to step back!

18
00:01:29,710 --> 00:01:31,660
No.

19
00:01:32,570 --> 00:01:35,010
How dare you!

20
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:16,420
Let me walk there on my own, Your Highness.

21
00:02:18,470 --> 00:02:20,380
Thank you...

22
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,630
for everything.

23
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:38,890
Scholar Sir!

24
00:02:38,890 --> 00:02:41,310
Why do you speak like that?

25
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:43,980
As if you will never see me again?

26
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,460
Withdraw your swords, all of you.

27
00:02:52,980 --> 00:02:56,490
Do not resist and follow, Supervisor Ha.

28
00:02:56,490 --> 00:02:59,200
Scholar Sir. Scholar Sir.

29
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:02,700
Scholar Sir. Scholar Sir! Scholar Sir!

30
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:05,100
You can't. No, don't do this!

31
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:08,130
Scholar Sir! Scholar—

32
00:03:10,850 --> 00:03:12,430
Scholar Sir!

33
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:14,720
Scholar Sir!

34
00:03:21,850 --> 00:03:23,630
Scholar Sir...

35
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:41,040
Make sure that woman gets home safely.

36
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,280
Yes, Your Highness.

37
00:03:57,820 --> 00:04:01,370
 Who is there? 

38
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:06,200
 I missed you... 

39
00:04:07,650 --> 00:04:09,840
 so much. 

40
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:21,070
♫  All the flowers in the world wither again  ♫

41
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:22,970
 I deeply cherish you. 

42
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:27,510
♫  Even if you lose that light when despair comes  ♫

43
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:29,800
 It seems 

44
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:33,550
 we are not meant to be together. 

45
00:04:33,550 --> 00:04:38,110
♫  Like a lie I will wait once more for my love.  ♫

46
00:04:38,110 --> 00:04:39,510
 Leave. 

47
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:41,180
 Far away from me. 

48
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:44,600
 I beg you. 

49
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:55,500
♫  Like a lie I will wait once more for my love.  ♫

50
00:04:55,500 --> 00:05:00,150
 Episode 11 
 Ring of Fate 

51
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:03,400
 Royal Investigation Bureau 

52
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:08,410
 Interrogations Confinement 

53
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:23,220
This is a special cell at the Investigation Bureau,

54
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:27,100
so you cannot leave, and you cannot meet with anyone.

55
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:30,680
It is becoming clear that you are the culprit who murdered the guards,

56
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:33,580
so stay here until the royal portrait is finished.

57
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:35,630
Yes, Your Highness.

58
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:41,840
- Step away for a moment.
 - Yes, Your Highness.

59
00:05:51,910 --> 00:05:57,010
The days have grown warmer, but the nights will still be cold.

60
00:05:57,010 --> 00:05:59,530
I shall have someone put in more hay.

61
00:05:59,530 --> 00:06:00,940
Your Highness.

62
00:06:00,940 --> 00:06:03,420
What is it?

63
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:07,710
Has Maiden Hong made it back safely?

64
00:06:08,770 --> 00:06:11,170
Do not worry. She did.

65
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:14,360
I had someone follow her and made sure she got back.

66
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:17,040
I apologize.

67
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:19,670
I feel...

68
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:21,980
I feel relieved.

69
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:25,680
I'm sorry.

70
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:33,100
Do you remember?

71
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:35,700
On the day we met for the first time in the palace,

72
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:40,830
I fell because I could not see and you helped me up

73
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:43,430
and you said,

74
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,370
"I'm sorry."

75
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:55,300
Why should Your Highness be sorry for my blindness?

76
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:57,550
For my crime?

77
00:06:57,550 --> 00:07:02,700
Why should Your Highness have to be sorry?

78
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:18,400
I should be going.

79
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:51,030
Did you get in trouble?

80
00:07:51,030 --> 00:07:53,140
What is it now?

81
00:08:01,130 --> 00:08:04,560
Did something happen?

82
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:07,730
No, nothing.

83
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:13,300
I heard Headmaster lectured you not to go to the palace for a while.

84
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:16,750
Is that why you are like this?

85
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:20,830
- How did you know?
 - I heard from Uncle Chunbok.

86
00:08:26,610 --> 00:08:29,300
Where on earth have you been?

87
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:32,000
Do you truly want to be locked up in the shed again?

88
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:35,510
- I keep telling you not to go to the Painting Bureau— 
 - Stop scolding—

89
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,830
- Cheon Gi!
 - Cheon Gi!

90
00:08:36,830 --> 00:08:37,940
- Cheon Gi!
 - Cheon Gi!

91
00:08:37,940 --> 00:08:38,850
Goodness, Cheon Gi!

92
00:08:38,850 --> 00:08:40,140
- Cheon Gi!
 - Cheon Gi!

93
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:42,190
Cheon Gi! Cheon Gi!

94
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,870
What do we do?

95
00:08:51,870 --> 00:08:53,920
She is as hot as coal.

96
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:57,690
Look, my daughter is dying.

97
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:04,680
But... where is my daughter?

98
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:06,660
Where did she go?

99
00:09:06,660 --> 00:09:08,620
Cheon Gi.

100
00:09:08,620 --> 00:09:11,710
- Cheon Gi!
 - She is right h...

101
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:32,040
 The scent of peach blossoms comes every spring 

102
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:37,550
 but I can no longer see the girl who was there. 

103
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:42,420
 The road of revenge, after I lost my sight, devoid of any warmth. 

104
00:09:42,420 --> 00:09:45,570
 When we met each other again, somewhere along that road, 

105
00:09:45,570 --> 00:09:49,480
 she made me who cannot see smile with a painting 

106
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:53,120
 and made me quiver like a branch in the wind. 

107
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,400
Ha Ram!

108
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:58,900
 The memories disappear and only nightmares remain. 

109
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:02,900
 It makes my heart ache. 

110
00:10:05,180 --> 00:10:08,200
 He says to prove our love by parting. 

111
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:11,930
 Is it a curse or retribution? 

112
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:15,490
 My cruel fate. 

113
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:18,880
 How miserable. So miserable. 

114
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:26,760
♫  I hope we don't pass each other like the passing wind.  ♫

115
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:32,070
♫  I am here.  ♫

116
00:10:59,130 --> 00:11:03,760
 Do you dare to attempt to paint me? 

117
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:24,220
 I will paint it. 

118
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:26,180
 No matter what. 

119
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:33,800
Father, it's time for your medicine.

120
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:35,770
Hush.

121
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:41,070
Father, here.

122
00:11:44,700 --> 00:11:46,570
Father.

123
00:11:47,370 --> 00:11:50,060
Father, you know...

124
00:11:52,010 --> 00:11:57,410
For the first time, I think I will have to...

125
00:11:58,550 --> 00:12:02,620
paint for someone else instead of you.

126
00:12:04,290 --> 00:12:06,270
Just this once.

127
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:10,740
Just this once, for the first and last time,

128
00:12:12,620 --> 00:12:15,700
I will paint for someone else.

129
00:12:16,810 --> 00:12:19,410
I will finish...

130
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:23,560
the painting that you once painted.

131
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:30,680
 Father. 

132
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:36,000
 Help me just this once. 

133
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,690
 So I can succeed. 

134
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:51,640
What is so serious that you made us lock the door?

135
00:12:53,180 --> 00:12:55,940
I will paint the royal portrait.

136
00:12:55,940 --> 00:12:58,400
- What?
 - Are you crazy?

137
00:12:59,210 --> 00:13:01,470
Why are you suddenly being like this?

138
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:07,590
The Scholar...

139
00:13:09,350 --> 00:13:11,420
Ma Wang is...

140
00:13:12,260 --> 00:13:13,860
inside Ha Ram's body!

141
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:15,690
I want to help somehow.

142
00:13:15,700 --> 00:13:18,800
What are you talking about? Supervisor Ha is a what?

143
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:22,500
Gosh. That doesn't make any sense.

144
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:25,010
The scholar was taken to the Investigations Bureau.

145
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:28,700
As a suspect in the guards' corpse incident at Inwang Mountain.

146
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:34,940
If I don't do anything, the scholar and other people could be in danger.

147
00:13:34,940 --> 00:13:37,380
I'm not sure of all the details.

148
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:41,900
Anyhow, I have to finish the royal portrait to save everyone.

149
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:44,390
You will be in danger if you finish the royal portrait.

150
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:45,670
Did you forget what Headmaster said?

151
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:47,520
Just look at your father.

152
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:49,580
I came here determined.

153
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:52,500
I beg you.

154
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:56,830
You two are my only friends.

155
00:13:57,520 --> 00:14:00,140
I beg you just this once.

156
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:15,400
 Interrogations Confinement 

157
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:21,400
Supervisor Ha of Astronomy and Meteorology Bureau.

158
00:14:31,420 --> 00:14:35,340
Ha of Astronomy and Meteorology Bureau...

159
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:37,870
So he has come all the way here.

160
00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:45,980
I suppose it is time for me to leave.

161
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:49,480
Leave us.

162
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:12,300
Have some. It is the sparrow tongue tea that you like.

163
00:15:16,450 --> 00:15:18,660
I apologize, Your Highness.

164
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:27,610
But, at least during the interrogation, please forget that we were friends.

165
00:15:41,230 --> 00:15:44,460
On the day of the Seokcheok Rain Ritual,

166
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:46,970
there was a fire at Gyeongwonjeon.

167
00:15:46,970 --> 00:15:51,600
I was looking at King Yeongjong's royal portrait with Hyeong-nim Juhyang then.

168
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:57,300
 Doesn't royal grandfather's portrait seem truly alive? 

169
00:15:57,300 --> 00:16:02,880
I suspect Ma Wang's seal was broken when the painting caught on fire

170
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:06,010
and it entered your body.

171
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:10,030
Is that so?

172
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:16,410
I cannot believe Ma Wang was inside you all this time...

173
00:16:17,690 --> 00:16:22,610
How long has Your Highness known this?

174
00:16:23,430 --> 00:16:26,780
I found out after the incident at Gyeongwonjeon.

175
00:16:26,780 --> 00:16:31,160
I still cannot forget how your nails grew longer

176
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:34,000
and the look in your eyes changed.

177
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:37,840
But you do not remember it.

178
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:40,610
Because it is not your memory.

179
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:46,080
If I had known this earlier,

180
00:16:46,930 --> 00:16:51,150
I would have bound myself in chains.

181
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:55,460
Are you admitting that you could harm someone

182
00:16:55,460 --> 00:16:59,350
every time you lose your memories?

183
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,790
Yes.

184
00:17:04,770 --> 00:17:06,380
I am.

185
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:11,850
You seem to realize how dangerous Ma Wang inside you is.

186
00:17:11,850 --> 00:17:14,060
So I will not ask further.

187
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:17,890
Now there is only one path left for you.

188
00:17:25,780 --> 00:17:28,160
Cooperate in the sealing ritual.

189
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:32,790
That is the best for all of us and for you.

190
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:37,480
 We must bring Ma Wang out from your body. 

191
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:39,690
 No matter what happens. 

192
00:17:39,690 --> 00:17:43,770
Then, I'd like to ask you one thing.

193
00:17:45,430 --> 00:17:46,780
Go ahead.

194
00:17:46,780 --> 00:17:49,850
Are you certain that a royal portrait is required for the sealing ritual?

195
00:17:49,850 --> 00:17:51,070
Yes.

196
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:55,380
But that royal portrait cannot be drawn by just anyone.

197
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:59,640
Unless they are a divine painter like Maiden Hong.

198
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:06,230
Her father became mad after finishing King Yeongjong's royal portrait.

199
00:18:06,900 --> 00:18:11,520
Can you be certain that this will not happen to her?

200
00:18:13,450 --> 00:18:16,430
- That is— 
 - If the royal portrait is mandatory for the ritual,

201
00:18:16,430 --> 00:18:19,790
I do not wish to proceed with it.

202
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:24,980
Do you believe that finishing the royal portrait will harm Painter Hong?

203
00:18:24,980 --> 00:18:27,780
I hear the painter who finishes King Yeongjong's royal portrait

204
00:18:29,220 --> 00:18:33,010
will be cursed at the sealing ritual.

205
00:18:33,010 --> 00:18:35,490
Just as Painter Hong Eun Oh was.

206
00:18:35,490 --> 00:18:37,900
Is that true?

207
00:18:37,900 --> 00:18:40,020
Yes, Your Highness.

208
00:18:40,020 --> 00:18:43,800
Will you still insist on finishing the royal portrait?

209
00:18:43,800 --> 00:18:46,330
If you truly care for the maiden,

210
00:18:46,330 --> 00:18:50,020
please stop the royal portrait re-creation.

211
00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:15,020
 Every time I lose my memory, the people I care about die. 

212
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:19,900
 Without the sealing ritual, he will be inside my body forever. 

213
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:22,800
 Ma Wang. Just why? Why? 

214
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:27,210
 Why are you inside me? 

215
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:07,070
You are here.

216
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:09,290
Are you all right?

217
00:20:09,290 --> 00:20:10,930
Yes.

218
00:20:10,930 --> 00:20:13,690
Do you blame me?

219
00:20:22,900 --> 00:20:25,230
That ring…

220
00:20:28,010 --> 00:20:30,680
The scholar gave it to me.

221
00:20:35,370 --> 00:20:38,030
I could not help it.

222
00:20:39,270 --> 00:20:43,470
- Yes.
 - I also feel horrible, but

223
00:20:45,040 --> 00:20:47,680
it had to be done.

224
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:53,290
For your sake as well.

225
00:20:59,600 --> 00:21:02,060
I will rest for a while.

226
00:21:10,090 --> 00:21:12,890
- Don't do this.
 - Let me ask you.

227
00:21:12,890 --> 00:21:15,730
What am I to you?

228
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:20,300
You are this nation's grand prince.

229
00:21:20,300 --> 00:21:25,400
I am asking you what I am to you as a man.

230
00:21:33,090 --> 00:21:35,560
Would you like me to be honest?

231
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:38,820
Tell me.

232
00:21:38,820 --> 00:21:41,140
A wretch.

233
00:21:47,370 --> 00:21:49,840
A wretch?

234
00:21:54,380 --> 00:22:01,580
♫  Do you see? My feeling for you  ♫

235
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:09,730
♫  Like destiny always cannot leave your side  ♫

236
00:22:09,730 --> 00:22:14,860
♫  On a day still like this, can you hug me?  ♫

237
00:22:14,860 --> 00:22:17,860
 Do you know what kind of star the Big Dipper is? 

238
00:22:17,860 --> 00:22:22,160
 It is the star that watches over all the good and bad, lucky and unlucky aspects of life 

239
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:25,110
 ever since a person is born, allotted a span of life, by Grandma Samshin. 

240
00:22:25,110 --> 00:22:31,040
 Then, is a person's destiny is decided at birth? 

241
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:36,490
 It is not easy to change the fate assigned to you. 

242
00:22:36,490 --> 00:22:40,230
 I suppose that is true. 

243
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:48,940
♫  I hope we don't pass each other like the passing wind.  ♫

244
00:22:48,940 --> 00:22:54,040
♫  I am here.  ♫

245
00:22:56,560 --> 00:22:58,380
Painter Hong?

246
00:22:59,410 --> 00:23:01,630
Painter Hong, are you here?

247
00:23:14,990 --> 00:23:17,430
 Goodness. 

248
00:23:17,430 --> 00:23:20,470
 When did she create a sketch like this? 

249
00:23:20,470 --> 00:23:22,380
Remarkable.

250
00:23:22,380 --> 00:23:26,820
It is as if I am seeing Royal Father alive.

251
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:32,280
Then, we shall now wrap up the sketch of the royal portrait.

252
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:34,340
Do so.

253
00:23:34,340 --> 00:23:38,890
Now then, the sangcho* must begin.
  (Process of putting final sketch on silk)  

254
00:23:38,890 --> 00:23:40,270
Yes, Your Majesty.

255
00:23:40,270 --> 00:23:43,430
Once the sangcho begins,

256
00:23:43,430 --> 00:23:46,990
any behavior that may bring bad luck must be forbidden.

257
00:23:46,990 --> 00:23:49,640
From now on,

258
00:23:49,640 --> 00:23:54,190
forbid the divine painter from leaving the palace.

259
00:23:54,190 --> 00:23:56,310
Yes, Your Majesty.

260
00:24:03,050 --> 00:24:04,560
What are we to do?

261
00:24:04,560 --> 00:24:06,530
If Master is interrogated

262
00:24:06,530 --> 00:24:09,980
and admits to a crime he did not commit,

263
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:12,780
everything will be ruined.

264
00:24:12,780 --> 00:24:17,540
We must gather all the information at Wolseongdang to save him.

265
00:24:19,360 --> 00:24:23,200
The master left this in case anything happened.

266
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:30,150
 If you are reading this letter, something has happened to me. 

267
00:24:30,150 --> 00:24:36,750
 Do not be alarmed. Deliver this letter to Grand Prince Juhyang through Mu Yeong. 

268
00:24:37,900 --> 00:24:43,250
Grand Prince Yangmyeong has arrested Supervisor Ha for the guards' murder incident at Inwang Mountain.

269
00:24:43,250 --> 00:24:46,230
- Yul did?
 - Yes.

270
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:51,640
 Has he found out about Ma Wang's existence? 

271
00:24:52,210 --> 00:24:57,190
Nothing must happen to Supervisor Ha until we transfer Ma Wang.

272
00:24:57,190 --> 00:25:02,690
But it seems Grand Prince Yangmyeong already knows.

273
00:25:02,690 --> 00:25:04,380
What do you mean?

274
00:25:04,380 --> 00:25:11,190
Grand Prince Yangmyeong has been the one to oversee the restoration of the royal portrait.

275
00:25:13,420 --> 00:25:16,100
How could that be?

276
00:25:17,020 --> 00:25:19,190
Royal Father…

277
00:25:19,190 --> 00:25:22,920
 Your Highness, there is a letter here for you. 

278
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:43,270
 I shall share the first method for Your Highness to seize the golden opportunity. 

279
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:53,530
So this is the map of the Investigations Bureau where the scholar is kept?

280
00:25:53,530 --> 00:25:55,020
Listen up.

281
00:25:55,020 --> 00:25:58,320
You go through the entrance, and there is the interrogation yard.

282
00:25:58,320 --> 00:26:03,570
Painters sit right here in the yard and paint the criminals' appearance.

283
00:26:03,570 --> 00:26:06,330
But other than that place, I have no idea about other places.

284
00:26:06,330 --> 00:26:09,470
No one answers me properly, even if I ask.

285
00:26:09,470 --> 00:26:11,390
What is this here?

286
00:26:11,390 --> 00:26:14,420
Now that is the cells.

287
00:26:14,420 --> 00:26:16,470
But this is only a normal cell,

288
00:26:16,470 --> 00:26:19,890
so if you give some money to the guards, they say you can go in.

289
00:26:19,890 --> 00:26:22,040
But the problem is...

290
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:24,210
Here. Here.

291
00:26:24,210 --> 00:26:25,770
What did they say again?

292
00:26:25,770 --> 00:26:29,200
Anyhow, it is a special cell built of rocks.

293
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:32,810
Here, not even the ordinary guards can approach.

294
00:26:32,810 --> 00:26:35,670
So all of that said, you think Supervisor Ha is in there?

295
00:26:35,670 --> 00:26:41,880
I asked anyone and everyone from everywhere, from every corner,

296
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:43,730
but no one knows.

297
00:26:43,730 --> 00:26:45,600
Then the answer is right here.

298
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:48,490
Here, it has to be the rock cell.

299
00:26:48,490 --> 00:26:50,140
They are locked away so secretly

300
00:26:50,140 --> 00:26:54,610
that no one knows whether they are dead or alive once they go in there.

301
00:26:54,610 --> 00:26:55,770
Right here.

302
00:26:55,770 --> 00:26:58,760
Then, how about a way to get in?

303
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:01,990
I found out all I could while I was at the Investigations Bureau.

304
00:27:01,990 --> 00:27:08,840
But unless you have a written command from the Grand Prince, there is no way in.

305
00:27:08,840 --> 00:27:12,250
Should we make it? The written command?

306
00:27:12,250 --> 00:27:13,520
Hey, hey.

307
00:27:13,520 --> 00:27:16,340
Stop talking nonsense and finish the royal portrait.

308
00:27:16,340 --> 00:27:17,820
He is right.

309
00:27:17,820 --> 00:27:21,580
That will be faster than sneaking in like this.

310
00:27:21,580 --> 00:27:25,290
I will finish the royal portrait, without a doubt.

311
00:27:25,290 --> 00:27:28,740
I could finish even faster if you both helped me.

312
00:27:28,740 --> 00:27:32,370
But didn't you say ordinary people couldn't paint it?

313
00:27:32,370 --> 00:27:34,790
What, you both are ordinary people?

314
00:27:34,790 --> 00:27:39,050
You are still painters who made it to the third round at Maejukheon Painting Contest.

315
00:27:39,050 --> 00:27:40,410
That is not it.

316
00:27:40,410 --> 00:27:45,450
He and I don't have that divineness. The divine power.

317
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:53,210
 The painting to seal Ma Wang, 

318
00:27:53,210 --> 00:27:55,270
 King Yeongjong's royal portrait. 

319
00:27:55,270 --> 00:27:59,260
 But not everyone can paint it. 

320
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:01,940
 How did Father do it? 

321
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:04,800
 Sealing Ma Wang. 

322
00:28:16,590 --> 00:28:18,050
That little girl ...

323
00:28:18,050 --> 00:28:20,290
 Can you see me? 

324
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:23,600
 As expected. Evil eyes. 

325
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:27,200
 Break up with Ma Wang now. 

326
00:28:33,360 --> 00:28:35,840
Hey.

327
00:28:35,840 --> 00:28:40,100
Little girl? I prepared some tea, the tea you like.

328
00:28:40,100 --> 00:28:42,300
Won't you come out and have some?

329
00:28:42,300 --> 00:28:45,890
I have forsythia tea, apricot tea, all of it.

330
00:28:53,140 --> 00:28:55,250
Hey, little girl—

331
00:28:56,860 --> 00:28:58,870
Excuse me.

332
00:28:59,870 --> 00:29:01,950
Excuse me.

333
00:29:07,230 --> 00:29:10,460
Who is the little girl here, baby?

334
00:29:10,460 --> 00:29:12,690
You scared me.

335
00:29:14,230 --> 00:29:17,720
I am Ho Ryeong of Inwang Mountain.

336
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:19,680
Ho Ryeong?

337
00:29:27,090 --> 00:29:30,300
So, you ... 
   *uses casual style with no honorifics)  

338
00:29:31,140 --> 00:29:32,830
I mean...

339
00:29:33,460 --> 00:29:41,130
So, Madam Ho Ryeong, you are a spirit from Inwang Mountain that guards the palace, yes?

340
00:29:41,130 --> 00:29:43,970
Have you finally figured that out, baby?

341
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:48,230
I must ask you something.

342
00:29:48,230 --> 00:29:51,700
- What?
 - You know how before...

343
00:29:51,700 --> 00:29:55,140
you told me to break up with Ma Wang…

344
00:29:55,140 --> 00:29:56,650
What does that mean?

345
00:29:56,650 --> 00:29:59,440
Oh, that?

346
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:03,530
I meant Ma Wang will chase you with every chance he gets,

347
00:30:03,530 --> 00:30:05,470
so stop seeing him.

348
00:30:05,470 --> 00:30:09,910
I'm not sure I understand what you…

349
00:30:09,910 --> 00:30:13,570
You could die.

350
00:30:13,570 --> 00:30:15,150
Pardon?

351
00:30:15,150 --> 00:30:18,790
What a dimwitted human.

352
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:23,060
How do you think you can see me?

353
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:25,370
What do you think is the reason that Ma Wang,

354
00:30:25,370 --> 00:30:29,860
who is a threat to you, keeps appearing in front of you?

355
00:30:31,610 --> 00:30:33,440
That's...

356
00:30:35,210 --> 00:30:40,220
Because I am the painter who will paint the royal portrait to seal him?

357
00:30:40,220 --> 00:30:41,530
Yes, that's it.

358
00:30:41,530 --> 00:30:46,920
That is why Ma Wang keeps manifesting every time you two touch.

359
00:30:50,690 --> 00:30:53,030
 Avoid him when you meet him. 

360
00:30:53,030 --> 00:30:55,780
 You never know when you could die. 

361
00:30:56,400 --> 00:31:01,600
 Watch yourself and finish the painting. 

362
00:31:12,690 --> 00:31:14,820
 What do you think is the reason that 

363
00:31:14,820 --> 00:31:19,010
 Ma Wang who is a threat to you keeps appearing in front of you? 

364
00:31:19,010 --> 00:31:21,000
Because of me...

365
00:31:22,140 --> 00:31:25,560
Ma Wang manifests because of me...

366
00:31:30,780 --> 00:31:33,770
What on earth is all that?

367
00:31:53,770 --> 00:31:58,070
- The struggle with the groundwork sketch is now over. 
 - Pardon?

368
00:31:58,070 --> 00:32:00,810
His Majesty was pleased with it.

369
00:32:00,810 --> 00:32:04,340
He ordered an auspicious date to be set,

370
00:32:04,340 --> 00:32:07,780
so you shall begin sangcho soon.

371
00:32:08,630 --> 00:32:14,180
And once sangcho begins, you must stay at the palace

372
00:32:14,180 --> 00:32:16,520
until the final version is finished.

373
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:22,100
You mean I cannot leave the palace?

374
00:32:22,100 --> 00:32:23,760
That is right.

375
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:28,660
You cannot meet anyone or go anywhere where you might attract negative energy.

376
00:32:30,650 --> 00:32:32,950
What is the matter?

377
00:32:34,810 --> 00:32:39,040
If I cannot leave the palace until the royal portrait is finished,

378
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:45,000
- please let me see the scholar again before I begin. 
 - What?

379
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:49,830
I think I could only focus on the painting once I make sure he is doing well.

380
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:51,190
No, I forbid it.

381
00:32:51,190 --> 00:32:54,200
Your Highness, just this once. I beg you.

382
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:55,650
Will you really behave this way?

383
00:32:55,650 --> 00:32:59,910
Even when you know that evil, vicious being is inside Supervisor Ha?

384
00:33:04,830 --> 00:33:10,250
I do not know how else to ask you for your help.

385
00:33:10,250 --> 00:33:14,540
- Get up.
 - I will not get up until you agree to help me.

386
00:33:14,540 --> 00:33:16,540
You truly...

387
00:33:22,290 --> 00:33:27,940
This is... truly unlike you.

388
00:33:27,940 --> 00:33:33,820
Your Highness, a painter's brush is said to be moved by her heart, rather than by her hand.

389
00:33:33,820 --> 00:33:38,630
Then, how much more so for King Yeongjong's royal portrait that must be infused with divine power?

390
00:33:38,630 --> 00:33:43,130
Shouldn't my heart be free from any trace of regret?

391
00:33:43,130 --> 00:33:45,500
So, please.

392
00:33:45,500 --> 00:33:50,440
Please let me see the scholar at least once.

393
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:52,620
I beg you.

394
00:33:53,290 --> 00:33:58,290
 Was her love for him this deep? 

395
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:13,710
 Grand Prince Juhyang, 

396
00:34:13,710 --> 00:34:17,990
 there was a message that the crown prince is in grave condition in the palace. 

397
00:34:17,990 --> 00:34:22,240
 Call the royal physician and confirm that the crown prince is unconscious 

398
00:34:22,240 --> 00:34:24,610
 and make this fact public. 

399
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:34,820
Are you Heo Yu, the physician in charge of treating the crown prince?

400
00:34:34,820 --> 00:34:37,900
Yes, Your Highness.

401
00:34:37,900 --> 00:34:43,020
I hear the crown prince's health has been deteriorating with each passing day.

402
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:45,340
I hear he is completely unconscious.

403
00:34:45,340 --> 00:34:47,450
P-Pardon?

404
00:34:47,450 --> 00:34:50,560
H-how did you…

405
00:34:50,560 --> 00:34:53,660
If the king tries to walk down the wrong path,

406
00:34:53,660 --> 00:34:56,350
it is the basic duty of one serving him to stop him.

407
00:34:56,350 --> 00:35:00,420
Why are you not giving His Majesty the proper counsel?

408
00:35:01,230 --> 00:35:04,160
Do you not realize what crisis the court will suddenly face

409
00:35:04,160 --> 00:35:07,670
if anything happens to the crown prince?

410
00:35:07,670 --> 00:35:09,060
That's...

411
00:35:09,060 --> 00:35:14,790
Will you continue to sit by and watch the current situation?

412
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:26,660
Now, His Majesty will change his mind, even if by a little.

413
00:35:26,660 --> 00:35:30,710
Would his mind change so easily?

414
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:34,360
The crown prince's illness is nothing new.

415
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:37,570
Isn't that why His Excellency Seong Jin Gi is making his move on my behalf?

416
00:35:37,570 --> 00:35:40,090
- But— 
 - Enough.

417
00:35:42,950 --> 00:35:47,670
I like Il Wol Seong's game plan.

418
00:35:48,620 --> 00:35:54,750
It is unlikely for the crown prince to regain his health now, is it not?

419
00:35:54,750 --> 00:35:59,010
He is confined to his bed and barely breathing.

420
00:35:59,010 --> 00:36:03,220
What would happen to this country if we continue to look on idly?

421
00:36:03,220 --> 00:36:06,110
But what can we do?

422
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:09,710
As royal physicians receiving salaries from the nation, how can we keep our mouths shut

423
00:36:09,710 --> 00:36:13,800
and look on with indifference without advising the king?

424
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:17,000
You mean I should prepare for the worst?

425
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:18,900
Yes, Your Majesty.

426
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:23,520
Not only is the crown prince's illness not improving,

427
00:36:23,520 --> 00:36:27,610
but he has also been unconscious for several days now.

428
00:36:27,610 --> 00:36:32,660
Now, you must think of the nation.

429
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:36,230
What do you think about this?
 (Seong Jin Gi, Minister of Personnel) 

430
00:36:36,230 --> 00:36:41,250
It is not a new matter, so it is not wise to judge hastily.

431
00:36:41,250 --> 00:36:48,690
However, I believe it is right to fend off possible chaos at court.
 (Kim Hong Seo, Left State Minister) 

432
00:36:48,690 --> 00:36:50,610
That is not all.

433
00:36:50,610 --> 00:36:58,360
If something happens to the crown prince before you can appoint the successor,

434
00:36:58,360 --> 00:37:04,400
a political war will ensue among the courtiers to maintain their power.

435
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:11,190
You speak as if you wish something does happen to the crown prince.

436
00:37:11,190 --> 00:37:14,190
That is absolutely not true, Your Majesty.

437
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:17,150
I am advising you with utmost loyalty.

438
00:37:17,150 --> 00:37:20,140
Please take it into consideration.

439
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:23,630
I fully understand your counsel.

440
00:37:23,630 --> 00:37:25,530
Let us leave it for now.

441
00:37:25,530 --> 00:37:28,230
Yes, Your Majesty.

