00:38:40,700 --> 00:38:47,910
♫  Even if every day is long and cold  ♫

449
00:38:47,910 --> 00:38:52,270
♫  I will still be here  ♫

450
00:38:52,270 --> 00:38:58,900
♫  Even if it is said the long wait is like a long slumber  ♫

451
00:38:59,990 --> 00:39:06,100
It was truly wise of you to set the physicians into action.

452
00:39:06,100 --> 00:39:08,920
Shouldn't we stoke the fire now?

453
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:10,370
Yes, Your Highness.

454
00:39:10,370 --> 00:39:14,690
The scholars who studied with me under the same teacher will lead their young students.

455
00:39:14,690 --> 00:39:21,630
It will be difficult for His Majesty to ignore the matter further.

456
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:29,560
Your Highness.

457
00:39:29,560 --> 00:39:34,670
Among the court officials, His Excellency Seong Jin Gi continues to bring up the appointment of next crown prince.
 (Sim Jeong Wu, Researcher at the Hall of Worthies) 

