00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:38,040
His Excellency  Seong Jin Gi is a long-time follower of Grand Prince Juyhang.
   

459
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:41,560
Why do you come to me, speaking of these disloyal matters?

460
00:39:41,560 --> 00:39:44,000
When His Royal Highness the Crown Prince is still well and alive.

461
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:45,810
Leave at once.

462
00:39:45,810 --> 00:39:49,130
- Your Highness.
 - I said leave!

463
00:39:54,990 --> 00:39:59,170
 Hyeong-nim, what do you want me to do? 

464
00:39:59,170 --> 00:40:02,260
 Just what am I supposed to do? 

465
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:10,110
So, things are moving as Master Il Wol Seong planned.

466
00:40:10,110 --> 00:40:11,060
Yes.

467
00:40:11,060 --> 00:40:14,640
The appointment of the next crown prince is being discussed at the royal palace.

468
00:40:14,640 --> 00:40:18,810
Whatever happens, we cannot turn back now.

469
00:40:18,810 --> 00:40:22,870
We shall see this revenge through to its bitter end.

