00:41:48,500 --> 00:41:52,520
 Outlining on the silk canvas based on the groundwork sketch is finally finished. 

475
00:42:13,490 --> 00:42:16,220
Apples do not fall far from the tree.

476
00:42:16,220 --> 00:42:19,920
She is truly a divine painter.

477
00:42:20,680 --> 00:42:22,500
What is the next step?

478
00:42:22,500 --> 00:42:27,030
Now that the outlining is finished, it is time to apply color.

479
00:42:27,030 --> 00:42:30,830
Coloring will consist of filling in the colors on the back of the silk canvas,

480
00:42:30,830 --> 00:42:34,530
and then, filling in the colors on the front.

481
00:42:34,530 --> 00:42:38,590
In about ten days, you shall be able to examine it and order any improvements to be made.

482
00:42:38,590 --> 00:42:40,240
All of you have worked hard.

483
00:42:40,240 --> 00:42:44,560
I shall reward Painter Hong separately.

484
00:42:44,560 --> 00:42:46,750
I am greatly honored, Your Majesty.

485
00:42:46,750 --> 00:42:51,620
Your Majesty, Grand Prince Yangmyeong is here.

486
00:42:58,540 --> 00:43:02,290
Good, I was about to summon you.

487
00:43:02,290 --> 00:43:07,440
In about ten days, King Yeongjong's royal portrait will be finished.

488
00:43:07,440 --> 00:43:11,920
Start preparing for the sealing ritual in time for the set date.
 (Wol Seon, 5th Head Shaman of the Royal Shamanist Bureau) 

